<HEADLINE> Celebrity Birthdays  </HEADLINE>
By The Associated Press	   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Celebrity birthdays for the week of Aug. 6-12
</P>
<P>
   Aug. 6: Actress Catherine Hicks (''Seventh Heaven'') is 49.
Singer Pat McDonald of Timbuk 3 is 48. Singer Randy DeBarge of
DeBarge is 42. Singer Geri Halliwell is 28. Actress Soleil Moon
Frye (''Punky Brewster'') is 24.
</P>
<P>
   Aug. 7: Singer B.J. Thomas is 58. Actor Wayne Knight (''3rd Rock
From the Sun'') is 45. Singer Bruce Dickinson of Iron Maiden is 42.
Actor David Duchovny is 40. Actress Charlize Theron is 25.
</P>
<P>
   Aug. 8: Actor Dustin Hoffman is 63. Actor Keith Carradine is 51.
Actor Donny Most (''Happy Days'') is 47. Musician Dennis Drew of
10,000 Maniacs is 43. Musician The Edge of U2 is 39. Musician Rikki
Rockett of Poison is 39. Rapper Kool Moe Dee is 38. Singer JC
Chasez of 'N Sync is 24. Singer Drew Lachey of 98 Degrees is 24.
Actress Countess Vaughn (''The Parkers'') is 22.
</P>
<P>
   Aug. 9: Comedian-director David Steinberg is 58. Actor Sam
Elliott is 56. Singer Benjamin Orr of the Cars is 45. Actress
Melanie Griffith is 43. Actress Amanda Bearse is 42. Rapper Kurtis
Blow is 41. Singer-actress Whitney Houston is 37. Actress Gillian
Anderson is 32. Rapper Mack 10 is 29. Actress Jessica Capshaw is
24.
</P>
<P>
   Aug. 10: Singer Jimmy Dean is 72. Singer Eddie Fisher is 72.
Singer Bobby Hatfield of the Righteous Brothers is 60.
Singer-musician Ian Anderson of Jethro Tull is 53. Actress Rosanna
Arquette is 41. Actor Antonio Banderas is 40. Musician Jon Farriss
of INXS is 39. Singer Neneh Cherry is 36. Actress Angie Harmon
(''Law &AMP; Order'') is 28. Singer Nikki Bratcher of Divine is 20.
</P>
<P>
   Aug. 11: Singer Joe Jackson is 46. Actor Will Friedle (''Boy
Meets World'') is 24. Rapper Chris Kelly of Kris Kross is 22.
</P>
<P>
   Aug. 12: Actor George Hamilton is 61. Actress Jennifer Warren is
59. Singer-musician Mark Knopfler of Dire Straits is 51. Singer Kid
Creole is 50. Rapper Sir Mix-A-Lot is 37. Actress Rebecca Gayheart
is 28. Musician Bill Uechi of Save Ferris is 25. Actor Casey
Affleck (''200 Cigarettes'') is 25. Actress Dominique Swain is 20.
</P>
