<HEADLINE> Singer Simon Ribs Ex-Senator Simon  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   CARBONDALE, Ill. (AP) -- Former Sen. Paul Simon received some
gentle ribbing from singer Paul Simon about the politician's recent
foray into music.
</P>
