Chuck Finley will be given an extra day off and is scheduled to
start Saturday's game against Anaheim. RHP Steve Woodard will pitch
the series opener with the Angels Friday. ... RHP Charles Nagy
(right elbow) rejoined the Indians and threw on the side.
</P>
