Cardenal in a group of Devil Rays' personnel who have flu-like
symptoms. ''This thing is coming on quick,'' Rothschild said. ...
2B Bobby Smith, sidelined since July 6 with a knee sprain, resumed
taking batting practice. ... 3B Aubrey Huff, promoted from Triple-A
Durham Tuesday, made his first major league start.
